# Walkthrough — Ramadan Tournament Improvements

## Build Verification ✅
- **1764 modules** transformed, **0 errors**
- Lazy-loaded chunks confirmed: `AdminLogin-Do39pv9i.js` (1.6 kB) and `AdminPage-i08yiCOl.js` (74.7 kB)
- CSS: 66.83 kB (gzip 11.4 kB)

---

## A. Security Fixes

### 1–2. JWT Auth Middleware
- **[NEW]** [auth.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/middleware/auth.js) — [verifyAdmin](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/middleware/auth.js#5-24) middleware validates JWT from `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- **[MODIFIED]** [auth.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/routes/auth.js) — Login now returns a signed JWT (24h expiry) instead of static string
- **[MODIFIED]** [teams.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/routes/teams.js), [matches.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/routes/matches.js), [settings.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/routes/settings.js) — All POST/PUT/DELETE routes now require [verifyAdmin](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/middleware/auth.js#5-24)
- **[MODIFIED]** [api.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/services/api.js) — Sends `Authorization: Bearer <token>` on all admin requests

### 3. Visit Rate Limiting
- **[NEW]** [rateLimitVisit](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/middleware/auth.js#32-52) middleware in [auth.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/middleware/auth.js) — IP-based, 1 visit per hour, auto-cleanup

---

## B. Code Quality

### 4. Centralized API Error Handling
- **[MODIFIED]** [api.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/services/api.js) — Single [request()](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/services/api.js#17-27) helper checks `r.ok`, throws on 4xx/5xx

### 5. Dead Code Removal
- Removed `isToday` field from [Match.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/server/models/Match.js)
- Removed 3 legacy routes: `toggle-today`, `PATCH date`, `PUT result`
- Removed 3 client functions: `toggleToday`, `updateMatchDate`, `saveResult`

### 6. Extracted GROUPS Constant
- **[MODIFIED]** [MatchesManager.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/components/MatchesManager.jsx) — Now imports from [tournament.config.js](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/tournament.config.js)

### 7–8. Inline Styles → CSS Classes
- **[REWRITTEN]** [GroupTable.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/components/GroupTable.jsx) — `gt-*` classes, removed `<style jsx>`
- **[REWRITTEN]** [MatchesSection.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/components/MatchesSection.jsx) — `msc-*` classes
- **[REWRITTEN]** [MatchHistory.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/components/MatchHistory.jsx) — `mh-*` classes
- **[REWRITTEN]** [HomePage.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/HomePage.jsx) — `hp-*` classes

