## C. Design Enhancements

| # | Feature | Implementation |
|---|---------|---------------|
| 9 | **Site footer** | Added to [HomePage.jsx](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/HomePage.jsx) with tournament name, subtitle, copyright |
| 10 | **Page transitions** | `page-fade-in` class with `fadeSlideIn` keyframe animation |
| 11 | **Skeleton loading** | [SkeletonLoader](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/HomePage.jsx#17-33) component with shimmer animation during initial data fetch |
| 12 | **Mobile admin nav** | CSS media queries `@600px` and `@380px` for responsive tab sizing |
| 13 | **Team avatars** | First-letter avatar in bracket tree and champion banner |

---

## D. Performance & UX

| # | Feature | Implementation |
|---|---------|---------------|
| 14 | **Auto-refresh** | `setInterval` polls every 60s for updated match data |
| 15 | **Stale-while-revalidate** | Background refresh doesn't reset loading state — users see stale data while new data loads |
| 16 | **CSS organization** | Added 800+ lines of modular, namespaced CSS (gt-*, msc-*, mh-*, hp-*) |
| 17 | **Lazy loading** | `React.lazy()` for [AdminPage](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/AdminPage.jsx#354-569) + [AdminLogin](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/AdminLogin.jsx#4-86) — separate chunks |
| 18 | **Dynamic SEO** | [useDocumentTitle](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/HomePage.jsx#10-16) hook updates `<title>` based on tournament name and phase |

